            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                        <ab>
                          <lb n="1"/>θαῦμα μέγ’ ἀνθρώποις
                          <lb n="2"/>πάντων <persName type="divine" key="Mater">Μάτηρ</persName> προδίκνυτι·
                          <lb n="3"/>τοῖς ὁσίοις κίνχρητι καὶ οἱ γον<lb 
                        break="no" n="4"/>εὰν ὑπέχονται· τοῖς δὲ π<lb 
                        break="no" n="5"/>αρεσβαίνονσι <w lemma="θιός">θιῶν</w> γέν<lb 
                        break="no" n="6"/>ος ἀντία πράτει. <space quantity="1" unit="character"/> πάντε<lb 
                        break="no" n="7"/>ς δ’ <w lemma="εὐσεβίης">εὐσεβίες</w> τε καὶ εὔγλωθ<lb 
                        break="no" n="8"/><surplus>ι</surplus>οι πάριθ’ ἁγνοὶ <space quantity="1" unit="character"/> <w lemma="ἔνθεος">ἔνθεον</w> ἐς
                          <lb n="9"/><rs type="institution" subtype="public_space" role="cult" key="naos" ref="#phaistos"><persName type="divine" key="Megale Mater">Μεγάλας Ματρὸς</persName> <w lemma="ναός">ναόν</w></rs>,
                          <lb n="10"/><w lemma="ἔνθεος">ἔνθεα</w> δ’ ἔργα γνωσῆθ’ ἀ<lb 
                        break="no" n="11"/>θανάτας ἄξια τῶδε <rs type="institution" subtype="public_space" role="cult" key="naos" ref="#phaistos"><w lemma="ναός">ν<lb 
                        break="no" n="12"/>αῶ</w></rs>. <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                          </ab>
                    </div>
                    <div type="commentary">
                        <p>L’epigramma, originariamente posto nel luogo di culto della dea, attesta l’esistenza di un altrimenti ignoto tempio della <foreign>Megale Mater</foreign> a Phaistos.</p>
                <p><emph>Elementi istituzionali o altri termini rilevanti</emph>: <ref type="inst" target="#naos"><foreign>naos</foreign></ref>.</p>
